dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents hydrography for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Milwaukee_HydroLine_YE2016.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.

dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://county.milwaukee.gov/mclio/geodata.html
This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
